    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini Dei eterni, anno incarnationis eius millesimo centesimo
                        LIII, secundo kalendas martii, indictione II, Christo actore. Manifesti
                        sumus nos <persName ref="#people/3215">Passavanti</persName> (quondam
                            <persName ref="#people/3216">Sismundi</persName>) et <persName
                            ref="#people/3225">Berta</persName> uxor, consensu mariti mei, notitia
                        vero <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Bennus"
                            >Benni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> (…), quia per hanc cartulam pro Dei timore et
                        nostrorum redemptione donamus et tradimus transacto iure proprietatis manu
                        rectoris et conductoris <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3209"
                            key="#Bridges/pontoons"><rs key="#Bridges/pontoons">pontis</rs> de
                                <placeName ref="#places/3200" key="#Bridges/pontoons"
                                >Ficiclo</placeName></orgName>, pro adiutorio illius operis
                        retinendo, qui conducitur et retinetur auxilio dei et de rectoribus
                                <orgName><rs key="#Hospitals">ospitalis</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals"
                            >Altipasti</placeName></orgName>. Nos vero nominative pro ipso ponte
                        reconciliando annualiter volo, et optamus unde perpetualis transactum facio
                        de duobus sol. pensone quia recipere solemus de nostra terra et <rs
                            key="#Mansi">masia</rs> illa <persName><name ref="Brunus Berre">Brunelli
                                Berre</name></persName> de <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/318"
                            >Paterno</placeName>. (Modo <persName><name ref="Passerinus"
                                >Passerinus</name></persName> gener eius tenet). Intregram ipsam
                        pensionem, et si non annualiter adimplere voluerint tenetores tunc ius et
                        dominium requirendi de illa masia costringendi, donamus rectoribus, ut in
                        perpetuum pensionem II sol. habeant expedite, et numquam removere. Et si
                        quis removere voluerit ab ipsa opera componat penam rectoribus sol. C (…).
                            <foreign>Maledizioni</foreign>. + Amen. + Amen. + Fiat. Factum fuit hoc
                        a <placeName ref="#places/3226">Montespertoli Lucardo</placeName>, in
                        presentia <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rainuccius Cascianellus"
                                >Rinucini Cascianelli</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Iallus de Montespertoli">Ialli de
                            Montespertoli</name></persName> et presbiteri illorum et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rainuccius">Rainucini</name> de <placeName
                                ref="#places/3227">Gangalandi</placeName></persName>
                        <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>. Signa manuum predictorum donatorum
                        Passavanti, Berte, qui ita rogaverunt fieri. Et alios duos soldos preter
                        istos quos sibi retinuerunt, post mortem istorum si absque legitimis filiis
                        vel filia obierint et in etate non devenerit, tunc in eadem opera pontis
                        remaneant. Et sic IIII sol. erunt. (S) Ego Benno <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notarius</rs> et iudex interfui, et ipsam Bertam interrogavi, et
                        cognita bona voluntate eius cartulam scripsi et hanc complevi. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
